==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sensori-volitional
<hw>Sen*so`ri-vo*li"tion*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>Concerned both in sensation and volition; --
applied to those nerve fibers which pass to and from the cerebro-spinal
axis, and are respectively concerned in sensation and volition.</def>
<rj><au>Dunglison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sensory</ent>⟦br⟧
